trans-unit.source: Represents a read-only collection of client script blocks that are contained within a Web Form or user control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en skrivebeskyttet samling av klienten Skriptblokkene som finnes i et webskjema eller kontroll under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem> object in the ClientScriptItemCollection class represents a `script` block that is contained in a document (a Web Form, Web server control, a content page, or a master page) at design time.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem>objektet i klassen ClientScriptItemCollection representerer en `script` blokken som finnes i et dokument (et webskjema, Web serverkontroll, innhold-siden eller en hoveddokumentet) under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner> class to set or examine client script elements that are contained in a Web Forms document on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>klassen for å angi eller undersøke klienten skriptelementer som finnes i et webskjema dokumentet utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Retrieve the collection of client script elements that are contained within the Web document by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hente samlingen av klienten skriptelementer som finnes i Web-dokumentet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: Add a client script element to the Web document by using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Legg til en klient skriptet elementet Web-dokumentet ved hjelp av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.AddClientScriptToDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: To add client script elements at run time, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager> class.
trans-unit.target: For å legge til klienten skriptelementer ved kjøretid, kan du bruke <xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.ClientScriptManager>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The ClientScriptItemCollection class represents script elements at design time that execute on the client.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > For ClientScriptItemCollection klassen representerer skriptelementer på utformingstidspunktet som kjøres på klienten.

trans-unit.source: Because the `script` elements that are generated for ClientScriptItemCollection objects are not run on the server, the elements do not contain the `runat="server"` attribute.
trans-unit.target: Fordi den `script` elementer som genereres for ClientScriptItemCollection objekter ikke er kjøres på serveren, elementene inneholder ikke den `runat="server"` attributtet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: If `clientScriptItems` is `null` (`Nothing` in Visual Basic) or does not contain any elements, the constructor initializes an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Hvis `clientScriptItems` er `null` (`Nothing` i Visual Basic) eller inneholder ikke noen elementer, konstruktøren initialisere en tom <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the items in the `clientScriptItems` array are used to set the items for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Ellers elementene i den `clientScriptItems` matrise brukes til å angi elementene for <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: The ClientScriptItemCollection constructor is typically used in classes that are derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren ClientScriptItemCollection brukes vanligvis i klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Visual designers implement the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A> method to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection> object for the client script elements in a Web document at design time.
trans-unit.target: Visual utviklere implementere den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>metode til å returnere et <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection>objekt for klienten skriptelementer i et Web-dokument under utformingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebFormsRootDesigner.GetClientScriptsInDocument%2A>

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem"></xref> elements used to initialize the collection.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.ClientScriptItem"> </xref> elementer som brukes til å initialisere samlingen.
